  "sections": [
    {
      "title": "WARGEAR OPTIONS",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "Any number of Tempestus Scions can each have their hot-shot lasgun replaced with one of the following*:",
          "items": [
            "1 flamer",
            "1 grenade launcher",
            "1 hot-shot volley gun",
            "1 meltagun",
            "1 plasma gun"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "1 Tempestus Scion equipped with a hot-shot lasgun can be equipped with 1 regimental standard (that model\u2019s hot-shot lasgun cannot be replaced).",
          "items": []
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "1 Tempestus Scion\u2019s hot-shot lasgun can be replaced with 1 hot-shot laspistol and 1 master vox.",
          "items": []
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "1 Tempestus Scion\u2019s hot-shot lasgun can be replaced with one of the following:",
          "items": [
            "1 hot-shot laspistol and 1 medi-pack",
            "1 hot-shot lasgun, 1 hot-shot laspistol and 1 medi-pack [that model's hot-shot lasgun cannot be replaced]"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "The Tempestor Prime\u2019s bolt pistol can be replaced with one of the following:",
          "items": [
            "1 plasma pistol",
            "1 command rod"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "* You cannot select the same weapon from this list more than once per unit."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "tagged_list",
          "label": "CORE",
          "items": [
            "Deep Strike , Leader FACTION: Voice of Command Tempestor Prime: While this unit contains a Tempestor Prime, ranged weapons equipped by models in this unit have the [SUSTAINED HITS 1] ability."
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "WARGEAR ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "Medi-pack: At the start of your Command phase , if the bearer\u2019s unit is below its Starting Strength , you can return up to D3 destroyed Tempestus Scions models to this unit. Regimental Standard: Add 1 to the Objective Control characteristic of models in the bearer\u2019s unit. Command Rod: While the bearer is leading a unit, that unit can be affected by up to two different Orders at the same time. Master Vox: Each time the OFFICER in the bearer\u2019s unit issues an Order , it can issue it to an eligible unit up to 24\" away."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "UNIT COMPOSITION",
      "entries": [
